Economy of Italy


Milan is the financial centre of Italy



Currency
Euro (EUR), except in Campione d'Italia (CHF)



Fiscal year

calendar year



Trade organisations

European Union, WTO, OECD, AIIB


Statistics


GDP
$1.850,735 trillion (nominal, 2016); $2.234,500 trillion (PPP, 2016)[1]


